## 6. Everything Else

- **AI:** Simple/narrow only — ship computers, data processing, assistants. No strong AI (so far).
- **Aliens:** Small stellar nations at the fringes; occasional trade and simple diplomacy. The giants are too focused on each other to care.
- **The Concord of Man:** The old unified polity. Its dissolution needs a name (candidates: the Discord, the Sundering) and a timeline.

